<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Account Rejection Notification</title>
    <style>
        /* Inline CSS */
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            padding: 30px;
        }
        .logo {
            display: block;
            margin: 0 auto;
            max-width: 100px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #007bff;
            font-size: 28px;
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        h2 {
            color: #444;
            font-size: 22px;
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        p {
            color: #444;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: justify;
        }
        .reason {
            color: #dc3545;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .footer {
            color: #777;
            font-size: 14px;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
        .notification-heading {
            color: #dc3545;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        /* Media Query for Mobile */
        @media only screen and (max-width: 480px) {
            h1 {
                font-size: 24px;
            }
            h2 {
                font-size: 20px;
            }
            .notification-heading {
                font-size: 20px;
            }
            p {
                font-size: 14px;
            }
            .footer {
                font-size: 12px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dd1rpkqom/image/upload/v1713812782/Logo/htufx0pzpqdah3v1mkqw.png" alt="College Logo" class="logo">
        <h1>Haldia Institute of Technology</h1>
        <h2>Department of Computer Science and Engineering - Data Science</h2>
        <h1 class="notification-heading">Account Rejection Notification</h1>
        <p>Dear <%= user.name %>,</p>
        <p>We regret to inform you that your student account registration request at Haldia Institute of Technology's Department of Computer Science and Engineering - Data Science has been rejected by the administrator.</p>
        <p>The reason for rejection is as follows: <span class="reason"><%= reason %></span></p>
        <p>If you have any questions or need further clarification, please feel free to contact our support team at [support email or contact details].</p>
        <p>Thank you for considering Haldia Institute of Technology. We appreciate your interest and hope to have the opportunity to welcome you in the future.</p>
        <p class="footer">Best regards,<br>Mr. Soumya Mukherjee,<br>Head of Department, Department of Computer Science Engineering (Data Science)</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
